description:
Danny recaps this week's #RHONY, which featured the end of the clambake, stolen lobsters, Lu fantasizing about jumping ship, plus Sonja's magazine launch and a v important couch story. Danny also gives some thoughts on this week's #RHOBH.


RHOBH: 43:50ish
